Nancy Lee Grahn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nancy_Lee_Grahn 0 Nancy Lee Grahn (born April 28, 1956) is an American actress known primarily for her work in daytime soap operas, portraying Julia Wainwright Capwell on Santa Barbara from 1985–93 and Alexis Davis on General Hospital since 1996.
